Text: Hello NomDePlume and thank you for uploading Chelsea Lately. Can you please tell me if this is the only website where you upload the show? Sometimes I have a hard time accessing the site, so I was wondering if you upload it somewhere else as well. Thanks.

I upload it to 3 other websites.  they won't let me type it in the comments, but you can do a google search for "kat torrents" and the top result will be one of the other sites. sign up for an account there, and send me a private message and i can tell you the other places.
